<p><font face="Arial Black" size="36"><b>Data Grids</b></font></p>
<p>Introducing the LiveCode Data Grid. Create fantastic tables in LiveCode with automatic column resizing, independent formatting, highlighting, editing and much more!</p>
<p></p>
<p><font face="Arial Black">60 Properties</font></p>
<p>Control the entire object direcly from your LiveCode scripts. With over 60 properties to control, your Data Grid can be customized to fit any application design.</p>
<p></p>
<p><font face="Arial Black">Fully Extendable</font></p>
<p>Add your own scripts to supplement the Data Grid's functionality and create even richer interfaces for your stacks!</p>